%h1.underline Zone Templates

%div{ :style => "display: none;" }
  #new-template
    Add a new zone template
  #edit-template
    Edit this zone template's information
  #delete-template
    Delete this zone template
  #missing-soa
    Zone templates without SOA records cannot be used when creating new zones.

%table.grid
  %tr
    %td
      = link_to prototip_info_icon('table_add.png', 'new-template'), new_zone_template_path
      = link_to 'New template', new_zone_template_path
    %td &nbsp;
  = render :partial => 'zone_template', :collection => @zone_templates